277
00:13:53,340 --> 00:13:54,310
Xia Jingshi,

278
00:13:55,280 --> 00:13:56,880
Tinatanong kita sa huling pagkakataon—

279
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:58,510
sino ang

280
