Gusto ko lang sabihin sayo

288
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:14,750
na iniisip ko noon

289
00:14:14,750 --> 00:14:15,670
lahat ng gusto ko

290
00:14:15,670 --> 00:14:17,000
ay ang pinakamahalaga,

291
00:14:17,120 --> 00:14:18,920
pero nung nawala ka, narealize ko

292
00:14:21,150 --> 00:14:22,750
ikaw ang pinakamahalaga.

293
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:24,600
Hindi ko talaga ginusto

294
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:25,440
para patayin ka.

295
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:29,410
Bigyan mo ako ng isa pang pagkakataon.

296
00:14:30,360 --> 00:14:31,890
Ayaw mo pa ring sabihin sa akin.

297
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:34,510
alam ko.

298
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:36,810
Kasalanan ko lahat noon.

299
00:14:36,810 --> 00:14:37,670
Kung ano man ang nangyari noon,

300
00:14:37,670 --> 00:14:38,270
kasalanan ko ang lahat.

301
00:14:38,270 --> 00:14:39,320
Ginawa ko lahat ng mali.

302
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:40,270
Alam ko na kahit anong sabihin ko ngayon

303
00:14:40,270 --> 00:14:41,040
ay walang silbi.

304
00:14:41,300 --> 00:14:42,230
Lahat ng hinihiling ko

305
00:14:42,630 --> 00:14:44,160
ay para bumalik ka sa akin.

306
00:14:44,550 --> 00:14:46,050
Hangga't babalik ka sa akin,

307
00:14:46,050 --> 00:14:47,450
Gagawin ko lahat ng hilingin mo.

308
00:14:47,750 --> 00:14:49,150
Kaya kong isuko ang lahat.

309
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:51,210
Pwede tayong maging tulad ng dati.

310
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:52,550
Magsimula tayo ulit.

311
00:14:52,910 --> 00:14:53,870
Magkasama tayong muli,

312
