387
00:20:22,270 --> 00:20:23,110
Kakaalis ko lang

388
00:20:23,110 --> 00:20:24,660
kay Xia Jingshi.

389
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:27,300
Malamang pagod ka lang.

390
00:20:29,030 --> 00:20:30,670
